text: Ernst Madland (21 February 1927 - 16 November 1984) was a Norwegian gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1952 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1927 births Category:1984 deaths Category:Norwegian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Norway Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Stavanger
